137
00:08:55.244 --> 00:08:56.828
Oh.

138
00:08:56.912 --> 00:08:57.931
There is an explanation
for that.

139
00:08:57.955 --> 00:08:59.164
Oh!

140
00:08:59.248 --> 00:09:00.999
You see. time's...

141
