209
00:12:01.638 --> 00:12:02.931
Well.

210
00:12:03.014 --> 00:12:05.684
Now that the irritating
illustrator is gone.

211
00:12:05.767 --> 00:12:07.853
I can concentrate on
navigating us through...

212
