237
00:13:24.846 --> 00:13:27.182
<i>♪ I'm makin' my way ♪</i>

238
00:13:27.265 --> 00:13:29.267
<i>♪ I'm makin' my way ♪</i>

239
00:13:29.309 --> 00:13:30.769
Whew.

240
00:13:30.852 --> 00:13:32.938
<i>♪ And I'd rather be ballin'.
but instead ♪</i>

241
00:13:33.021 --> 00:13:36.066
