242
00:13:36.149 --> 00:13:38.485
<i>♪ I'm makin' my way ♪</i>

243
00:13:38.568 --> 00:13:42.239
<i>♪ I'm makin' my way ♪</i> ♪

244
00:13:44.950 --> 00:13:46.326
E-Easy. easy. whoa. Whoa.

245
00:13:46.409 --> 00:13:48.328
Hey. I got you. pal.

246
